:::'''Lady Vermilion:''' What do I do? What do I do? Ooh, I'm just about to tear my feathers out, tweet.
:::'''Lady Vermilion:''' I dozed off for a moment, and the birds were nowhere to be seen, tweet.
:::{{DIcon|Arrow}} What are you doing here?
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_503070404-->
::;(If {{cx}}<!--performance 414030301 has been seen-->)
::::'''Lady Vermilion:''' Oho, a familiar customer. Did you come all this way to see me? Tweet tweet?
::::'''Lady Vermilion:''' If you had come another time, I'd definitely show you a good time that you wouldn't soon forget, tweet.
::::'''Lady Vermilion:''' But I've something urgent to attend to. You'll have to make do and wait for me, tweet.
::::{{DIcon|Arrow}} You misunderstand.
:::::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_503070411-->
:::::The bird's eyes show a sliver of hurt out of nowhere &mdash; even you're hard-pressed to deny it.
:::::'''Lady Vermilion:''' Boohoo, so you didn't come here for me. I really do need your help, though, tweet.
::::{{DIcon|Arrow}} I've got some time.
:::::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_503070414-->
:::::The bird directs its watery big eyes at you, as if it'd cry in sheer gratitude.
:::::'''Lady Vermilion:''' So you do really care about me. Once I round up those little ones, I'll be sure to accompany you on your tour around Dreamville, tweet.
::::{{DIcon|Arrow}} Tell me about this unforgettable experience.
:::::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_503070417-->
:::::'''Lady Vermilion:''' Oh, this? Even three days wouldn't be enough if I went into detail, tweet.
:::::'''Lady Vermilion:''' I absolutely won't let you down, tweet.
::;(If {{cx}}<!--performance 414030301 has not been seen-->)
::::'''Lady Vermilion:''' Ooh, you've shown up just in time. Have you specially come to comfort me? Tweet tweet?
::::'''Lady Vermilion:''' While you weren't around, I missed you so much that even a few of my feathers fell out. My wings look worse for wear too, tweet...
::::'''Lady Vermilion:''' Now that I'm in big trouble, you must help me out, tweet.
:::<!--Custom String Trigger: Wait_Option_503070005_288-->
:::<!--Custom String Listener: Wait_Option_503070005_288-->
:::{{DIcon|Arrow}} What is this place?
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_503070420-->
:::'''Lady Vermilion:''' This is the Dreamgood Theater, where birds sing and melodies glide and mingle, tweet.
:::'''Lady Vermilion:''' Miss Note sometimes performs here too, where she teaches the birds the art of song. It's also the reason the theater's always packed with audiences from afar, tweet.
:::'''Lady Vermilion:''' I was watching the kids while Miss Note was giving singing lessons, but I lost concentration for just a moment, and they all disappeared, tweet.
:::'''Lady Vermilion:''' They're all energetic children. If they disturbed other guests, the Professor would be mad if he knew.
:::'''Lady Vermilion:''' Honored guest, would you bear to see an adorable bird shed tears because of this? Tweet tweet?
:::{{DIcon|Arrow}} Go do it yourself.
::::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_503070426-->
::::'''Lady Vermilion:''' Oh dear, wouldn't they miss me if birds came back looking for me? Tweet tweet?
:::{{DIcon|Arrow}} All right, I'll help you.
::::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_503070428-->
::::'''Lady Vermilion:''' I knew it! You wouldn't abandon me in the time of need. You're like my knight in shining armor in the stories, tweet.
:::{{DIcon|Arrow}} (Pretend not to hear)
::::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_503070430-->
::::'''Lady Vermilion:''' Honored guest, it's just you and me here. It's pointless even if you pretend not to hear me, tweet!
:::<!--Custom String Trigger: TalkSentence_503070431-->
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_503070431-->
