::::::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_Option-->
::::::{{DIcon}} About yourself...
:::::::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_503070503-->
:::::::'''Lady Vermilion:''' Oh dear, are you really that interested in me? The little birds call me Lady Vermilion, tweet.
:::::::'''Lady Vermilion:''' As Professor Owl's student, whether it's the elegant Blues Street, or the soothing garden, all the beautiful things you see in town are of my design, tweet.
::::::;(Return to previous option selection (cloneCheckString))
::::::{{DIcon}} Tell me the story of the origami birds...
:::::::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_503070506-->
:::::::'''Lady Vermilion:''' As the saying goes: To know a bird, you must start from its past. You're really sweet to do that, tweet.
:::::::{{DIcon|Arrow}} About the Dreamgood Theater...
::::::::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_503070508-->
::::::::'''Lady Vermilion:''' It's even said that the Dreamgood Theater already existed before Professor Owl even established Dreamville, tweet.
::::::::'''Lady Vermilion:''' Boss Stone and his minions keep insisting that their ancestors built the theater first. I say poppycock to that, tweet!
::::::::'''Lady Vermilion:''' Any way you look at it, this magnificent theater is a place meant for birds to flock together to sing, tweet.
:::::::;(Return to previous option selection (cloneCheckString))
:::::::{{DIcon|Arrow}} About the townspeople...
::::::::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_503070512-->
::::::::'''Lady Vermilion:''' The folks in Dreamville are good people, good birds. Even if their tempers are eccentric, tweet.
::::::::'''Lady Vermilion:''' I envy Miss Note the most &mdash; when she sings, all the conflicts in town go silent. And she's helped out a lot in educating the birds, tweet.
::::::::'''Lady Vermilion:''' If I had a voice as beautiful as hers, I could definitely attract more visitors to Dreamville, tweet.
:::::::;(Return to previous option selection (cloneCheckString))
:::::::{{DIcon|Arrow}} About Professor Owl...
::::::::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_503070516-->
::::::::'''Lady Vermilion:''' If there's anyone who knows "beauty" better than anyone in Dreamville, Professor Owl's the one and only expert, tweet.
::::::::'''Lady Vermilion:''' Which stones are good for building houses, and which branches can be used to adorn nests with flowers... Professor Owl's designs perennially capture the essence of beauty, allowing every little pebble to shimmer and shine, tweet.
::::::::'''Lady Vermilion:''' I hope one day in the future, I can also build a nest that's just as pretty, tweet.
:::::::;(Return to previous option selection (cloneCheckString))
::::::{{DIcon}} I need a few hints.
:::::::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_503070520-->
::::::;(If {{cx}}{{subst:void|<!--{"$type":"RPG.GameCore.ByCheckColonyTrace","ColonyID":{"IsDynamic":false,"FixedValue":{"Value":9}},"Inverse":true}-->}})
::::::::'''Lady Vermilion:''' Oh, I would love to help you, but I can't remember where they went either. Tweet...
::::::::'''Lady Vermilion:''' Dear guest, it'd be fantastic if you have a "magic coin." Magic coins can reawaken my memories, tweet!
